@loic-sharma mentioned:  NuGet client will try the "primary" search endpoint, and if that fails, retry on the "secondary" search endpoint. 
@zivkan helped finding the fallback at: https://github.com/NuGet/NuGet.Client/blob/dev/src/NuGet.Core/NuGet.Protocol/Resources/PackageSearchResourceV3.cs#L113
But it doesn't seem to retry:
https://github.com/NuGet/NuGet.Client/blob/dev/src/NuGet.Core/NuGet.Protocol/Resources/PackageSearchResourceV3.cs#L174
Haven't investigated more. Just create this in case we forget about it.
